				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I feel bad for the mages :(
<br />

<br />
While there is some justification for the nerf - one mage quoted roughly 280 mana per tick doing this - this is the case only for very high end mages with VT or time gear.
<br />

<br />
The way they are nerfing it basically affects *all* mages - even those who only see a slight benefit over meding.
<br />

<br />
They really should find a way to make this remain a useful way of gaining mana, without being overpowered for mages with end game gear.
<br />

<br />
-Kryq</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
