Why is there anything to be given in return?  Return for what?  Something not working as obviously intended?  Obviously exploited by some mages for how long now?  THey have mod rods - distributable canni that you charge up during downtime/preptime.  Wizzies can harvest (whee).  Maybe give wizzies some extra mana regen?  Mages can improve pet dps with pet items (haste/procs).  They can top up focus for those that need whichever one.  Boo-hoo, they wont outdps wizzies after its fixed (well, in the high-end).  They are still rediculously useful.
<br />

<br />
Compensation for an exploit fix?  How about nerfing mage mana regen by making voq/kei not stick to them for a year or so to compensate for the pet canniing?  And while they are reverse-compensating, I'd like my bear to be shrunk to gerbil-size when they grow gators ...  <img src="images/smiles/icon_lol.gif" alt="Laughing" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
