I agree, yet disagree...
<br />

<br />
Yes magi pets should do more damage then pet-canni can..  but I think the developers should do a full, 100% nerf on pet canni (nerf being limited to returning at max 100% mana spent, and not nerfing reclaim energy entirely)...
<br />

